<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">هـ ت ف:</span> <span class="c2">(الْهَتْفُ)</span> الصَّوْتُ،<span class="c5"> يُقَالُ:</span> <span class="c2">(هَتَفَتِ)</span> الْحَمَامَةُ مِنْ بَابِ ضَرَبَ. وَ <span class="c2">(هَتَفَ)</span> بِهِ صَاحَ بِهِ، يَهْتِفُ بِالْكَسْرِ <span class="c2">(هِتَافًا)</span> بِكَسْرِ الْهَاءِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>